# RISE website — environment variables
#
# All values are optional. Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and
# set what you need. Never commit real secrets — only this example file is
# tracked.
#
# Forms currently persist to a local filesystem store (`data/`, git-ignored)
# and notifications are recorded as files instead of emails. Hosted services
# (Supabase for storage, Resend for email, Sanity for content, Turnstile for
# spam protection) swap in later behind the seams in `lib/db/index.ts` and
# `lib/notify/index.ts`; their keys will be documented here when added.

# Where the filesystem store writes its data. Defaults to `./data`.
# RISE_DATA_DIR=

# Recipient recorded on new-submission notifications.
# RISE_NOTIFY_EMAIL=

# Password for the admin views. The admin area is disabled when unset.
# Use a high-entropy value (e.g. 32+ random characters): it is the entire
# admin auth surface and the session-signing key is derived from it.
# ADMIN_PASSWORD=
